The paper discusses the security challenges of location-based social network services, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of data analysis and machine learning techniques to detect location cheating, which could fall under the categories of social and information systems (cs.SI), control systems (cs.SY), cybernetics (cs.CY), and multimedia (cs.MM).
